# ML Services Directory

This directory will contain the Python/FastAPI ML services.

## Structure
```
ml-services/
├── src/
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── yield_prediction/    # Yield prediction models
│   │   ├── price_forecasting/   # Price forecasting models
│   │   └── crop_recommendation/ # Recommendation engine
│   ├── data/                    # Data processing
│   ├── api/                     # FastAPI endpoints
│   └── utils/                   # Utilities
├── notebooks/                   # Jupyter notebooks
├── tests/                       # Test files
├── models/                      # Trained models
└── requirements.txt             # Dependencies
```
